quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,44,"Am tahsabu anna aktharahumyasmaAAoona aw yaAAqiloona in hum illa kal-anAAamibal hum adallu sabeela"
  25,45,"Alam tara ila rabbika kayfa madda aththillawalaw shaa lajaAAalahu sakinan thumma jaAAalnaashshamsa AAalayhi daleela"
  25,46,"Thumma qabadnahu ilaynaqabdan yaseera"
  25,47,"Wahuwa allathee jaAAala lakumuallayla libasan wannawma subatan wajaAAalaannahara nushoora"
  25,48,"Wahuwa allathee arsala arriyahabushran bayna yaday rahmatihi waanzalna mina assama-imaan tahoora"
  25,49,"Linuhyiya bihi baldatan maytanwanusqiyahu mimma khalaqna anAAaman waanasiyyakatheera"
  25,50,"Walaqad sarrafnahu baynahumliyaththakkaroo faaba aktharu annasiilla kufoora"
  25,51,"Walaw shi/na labaAAathna feekulli qaryatin natheera"
  25,52,"Fala tutiAAi alkafireenawajahidhum bihi jihadan kabeera"
  25,53,"Wahuwa allathee maraja albahraynihatha AAathbun furatun wahatha milhunojajun wajaAAala baynahuma barzakhan wahijranmahjoora"
  25,54,"Wahuwa allathee khalaqa mina alma-ibasharan fajaAAalahu nasaban wasihran wakanarabbuka qadeera"
  25,55,"WayaAAbudoona min dooni Allahi mala yanfaAAuhum wala yadurruhum wakanaalkafiru AAala rabbihi thaheera"
